'From Squeak3.7alpha of ''11 September 2003'' [latest update: #5623] on 10 January 2004 at 3:29:59 pm'!"Change Set:		OrderedCollectionTestDate:			10 January 2004Author:			stephane ducassea place to write other tests on collection"!TestCase subclass: #OrderedCollectionTest	instanceVariableNames: ''	classVariableNames: ''	poolDictionaries: ''	category: 'Collections-Sequenceable-Test'!!OrderedCollectionTest methodsFor: 'testing-public methods' stamp: 'sd 1/10/2004 15:28'!testAddBefore	"self run: #testAddBefore"	| l |	l := #(1 2 3 4) asOrderedCollection.	l add: 88 before: 1.	self assert: (l =  #(88 1 2 3 4) asOrderedCollection).	l add: 99 before: 2.	self assert: (l =  #(88 1 99 2 3 4) asOrderedCollection). ! !!OrderedCollectionTest reorganize!('testing-public methods' testAddBefore)!